{
  "stem": "1479.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because after the liberation-- the children born to us after the liberation, they became the justification to continue life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Their existence, their achievements, was our triumph.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we only hope and pray that they will continue the Jewish tradition from generation to generation with pride, dignity befitting our people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We already, a little bit, are stepping aside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are permitting the second generation to carry on the tradition, to carry on to remember the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Holocaust was the most shameful tragedy since men walked on Earth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have no excuse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not only-- this does not only rest on our shoulders, but all Jews have the responsibility to carry on, never to forget what happened.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they are millions, hundreds, thousands, hundreds of thousands of names that nobody was left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There is nobody even to say a prayer after them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, my husband and I, when we settled in the United States, in the beginning it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You must remember how difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We experienced such unbelievable horrors, such deprivations, that it left permanent scars on our bodies and on our souls.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And yet, the world did not want to hear us, nobody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, we relied on ourselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we tried to carry on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It became like our life obligation to share our experience with many people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mainly, we are trying to reach the young people because today, they are students.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to remember, tomorrow, they are our future leaders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by sharing our opinion, by knowing what happened, and more you know, more you want to learn about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By knowing you would be and will be able to prevent from happening again because since it happened, a tragedy like that must not happen again.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About [?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
